	<dl>
	<dt>I am an very poor  ex-student, with ...</dt>
	<dd><p>I am an very poor  ex-student, with thousands of pounds of unpayable debt. I want to vote, but if I register I fear  that the bailiffs will come round and repossess my personal computer and anything else of value I own, and I'm too poor to replace those things. </p>
	<small>
	written 24th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1435">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1435">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

